# Burn-in scenario fixture targets — disposable, never committed.
# burn-in-10 creates files under tmp/burn-in/ inside an isolated
# workspace; the auto-reject path keeps source untouched, but this
# is a defense-in-depth so an accidental approval cannot land them.
tmp/burn-in/
